### Movie Management API Examples
### Make sure to start the server with: npm run dev
### Server should be running on http://localhost:3000

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:3000/health

###

### Get All Media with Pagination
GET http://localhost:3000/api/media?page=1&limit=5

###

### Search Media by Title
GET http://localhost:3000/api/media?search=inception

###

### Filter by Type (Movies only)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/media?type=MOVIE&limit=20

###

### Filter by Genre
GET http://localhost:3000/api/media?genre=SCIENCE_FICTION

###

### Filter by Year
GET http://localhost:3000/api/media?year=2010

###

### Advanced Filtering with Multiple Parameters
GET http://localhost:3000/api/media?type=MOVIE&genre=CRIME&sortBy=rating&sortOrder=desc&limit=10

###

### Get Single Media Item (replace :id with actual ID)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/media/1

###

### Create New Movie
POST http://localhost:3000/api/media
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "The Dark Knight",
  "type": "MOVIE",
  "director": "Christopher Nolan",
  "budget": 185000000,
  "location": "Chicago, USA",
  "duration": 152,
  "year": 2008,
  "genre": "ACTION",
  "rating": 9.0,
  "description": "When the menace known as the Joker wreaks havoc and chaos on the people of Gotham, Batman must accept one of the greatest psychological and physical tests.",
  "language": "English",

}

###

### Create New TV Show
POST http://localhost:3000/api/media
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Game of Thrones",
  "type": "TV_SHOW",
  "director": "David Benioff",
  "budget": 15000000,
  "location": "Northern Ireland",
  "duration": 57,
  "year": 2011,
  "genre": "FANTASY",
  "rating": 9.3,
  "description": "Nine noble families fight for control over the lands of Westeros, while an ancient enemy returns after being dormant for millennia.",
  "language": "English",

}

###

### Update Media Item (replace :id with actual ID)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/media/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rating": 9.5,
  "description": "Updated description with more details about the plot and characters."
}

###

### Partial Update - Only Rating
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/media/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rating": 8.9
}

###

### Delete Media Item (replace :id with actual ID)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/media/1

###

### Get Statistics Overview
GET http://localhost:3000/api/media/stats/overview

###

### Error Testing - Invalid Data
POST http://localhost:3000/api/media
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "",
  "type": "INVALID_TYPE",
  "year": 1800,
  "rating": 15
}

###

### Error Testing - Non-existent Media
GET http://localhost:3000/api/media/99999

###

### Error Testing - Invalid ID Format
GET http://localhost:3000/api/media/abc